div.p:
258. Your 144, July 9, 3 p.m.,Not printed;
                                it quoted telegrams exchanged with the Ambassador in Great Britain;
                                paragraph referred to is also the penultimate paragraph of telegram
                                no. 189, July 7, to the Ambassador in Great Britain, p. 466. penultimate paragraph,
                            your 145, July 9, 4 p.m., and my 230, July 12, 3 p.m., especially
                            paragraph 5.
